# Base URL for apps/studio-worker HTTP API (immersive-studio serve).
# Local: http://127.0.0.1:8787
# Production (Immersive Labs): set before `vite build` — VITE_* is inlined at compile time.
# VITE_STUDIO_API_URL=https://api.immersivelabs.space
#
# Worker must list your site origin(s) in STUDIO_CORS_ORIGINS (comma-separated), e.g.
#   https://immersivelabs.space,https://www.immersivelabs.space
VITE_STUDIO_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
